如，抛掷两枚硬币，样本空间 ｛正正，正反，反正，反反｝中的基本事件是等可能的，但样本空 间｛两正，一正一反，两反｝却不是等可能的．虽然取什么样本空 间不影响所考察的随机事件的概率，但只有选取等可能的样本 空间，才能使得事件的概率如定义所示，等于事件元素个数与 样本空间元素个数之比，进而使有关计算变得简单，所以我们 通常要选取一个等可能的样本空间．","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 105/在上一节说过，随机现象的样本空间的选取依赖于观察的 角度，但其中事件的概率与观察角度这一主观因素无关，是确 定唯一的．在古典概率模型中，随着观察角度的不同，并非所 有的样本空间都有等可能性．例如，抛掷两枚硬币，样本空间 ｛正正，正反，反正，反反｝中的基本事件是等可能的，但样本空 间｛两正，一正一反，两反｝却不是等可能的．虽然取什么样本空 间不影响所考察的随机事件的概率，但只有选取等可能的样本 空间，才能使得事件的概率如定义所示，等于事件元素个数与 样本空间元素个数之比，进而使有关计算变得简单，所以我们 通常要选取一个等可能的样本空间．.md","line":70},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/4UyZqOohhiGfKIXrUWpFMufrWo-DuAbKPFCiIn8XRg6ePgneg0kXYHxa5WRqr6ap_GvzCP2lVtxBd543EOlS98-iXFJOGD-CVsc9xpWo-Zz-BY6HbTpYif4DENlprwZz.png","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 106/Untitled.md","line":72},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/uwabctsOf6nUwmq7eO9KOuHCaWP7AjeD1qutm35_pq93Y3Oj2YE7sC3NVSpxiVO-WrOs_DrsSw7geyRok01Byo8VSsFHlaY8xrxJILXxdjEK2x8vA9tjKAgzEgWIrnkt.png","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 106/Untitled.md","line":74},{"title":"对于一个随机现象而言，在确定样本空间之后，事件对应于 样本空间的一个子集，通常用相同的字母来表示事件与相应的 子集．","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 107/对于一个随机现象而言，在确定样本空间之后，事件对应于 样本空间的一个子集，通常用相同的字母来表示事件与相应的 子集．.md","line":80},{"title":"互斥","target":"../../../互斥.md","line":96},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/TcI8qS4rqjaTDsFIYZ0LOWD9DDYpjDTa2VFjtCciflkWR5F-UQvDmd58--1VGQOgD8uzlwk_dZPNIaJW_OUku7O-pfDHVJt1Y9hj-6KDpxflZ5P_zKpJ_07IavoyRgya.png","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 108/Untitled.md","line":103},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/wC379jq-hH1y-wxlV7h9q44Zh0Bn7lwTmfqTfS4n1r8jiKfQrAGWSIx4Grlv-W2UV-zLCfjIUKgxOmI3eTP8pshZajBLFJhNdRikz52iW7gB6C3FN24lhrmguM5yHMIE.png","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 109/Untitled.md","line":104},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/ONQLJkhBTXnEK9kEfx817xxT5uCzhwuKv5M-53m2idoi8vQmthWPEpIlXMbfayETY0QuimaZwAHv6SAesop4_-Dvul_0QW0sP2WswWa1SqHShUz-5l7NFFTAsmJ4bkD1.png","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 110/Untitled.md","line":111},{"title":"可加性","target":"../../../可加性.md","line":111},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/2ba7C5vduK7wvVRkpaCzEf0vUHULQzckhDbLQX6dhcuCiz0-iP9GnLu_1Ig13XRoZlxWGX4dIJAfvr7OZG38ietbHVkh_I-i4qE6qJY5iIZDxONwin4lOifUMU7y0uR0.png","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 110/Untitled.md","line":125},{"title":"3．概率的性质","target":"../../../【精进】高二秋季10概率（教师版）/Highlights/Page 06/3．概率的性质.md","line":127},{"title":"运算","target":"../../../运算.md","line":127},{"title":"前面所讲的古典概率是概率的特殊情况和思想源泉，但应该 指出，概率不限于古典概率","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 111/前面所讲的古典概率是概率的特殊情况和思想源泉，但应该 指出，概率不限于古典概率.md","line":134},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/8rvor-HrwXag9avY3iV0V5BMb2VRGtGU3opfv7fSdU0cGFsm_FTW3pmGLf6wr-rI6PcSZpx3Q_3L8wvH1iilp79rUjPY5opnshfszl4TJMDNUDuRlQ1OUGB3OMVA9df_.png","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 111/Untitled.md","line":136},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/iHqz1Y_ChaHmFgNbdhVe-EHtW7Pi2LHl4_6ECtnWr4jFdv9hqg3q4zJ2SO_2HgPsk5Ex1LPksHaMzE2L9S922AaovRe1qyc8ulonzhrwd6QZFaDpiQclBS9-oOvlfTes.png","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 111/Untitled.md","line":138},{"title":"对称","target":"../../../对称.md","line":139},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/RgPIzhw_WVjotKYuIVIM8qbnX78-HRbTpepTmkBVJbPMq40kyUD0I9TKEucXI5lVzuqFYPwPT8bIgh2ZcSHinN2cz-m4qgqPYZjONCCeJ9vaSaebhX2mlONbAcT14Lbu.png","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 112/Untitled.md","line":146},{"title":"随机事件的独立性","target":"../../../必修三/Highlights/Page 119/随机事件的独立性.md","line":150}],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"1b25xvx","at":1769676521235}},
